on these shelves

21:37.233 --> 21:39.166
is new to someone
who hasn't read it.

21:39.233 --> 21:42.367
- You know, Blake,
he said,

21:42.433 --> 21:46.400
"There is a moment in each day
that Satan cannot find."

21:46.467 --> 21:47.800
- That's right.

21:47.867 --> 21:50.166
You know what
my ultimate goal is?

21:50.233 --> 21:55.166
To make that moment
last a lifetime.

22:00.567 --> 22:02.667
- Libros.

22:02.734 --> 22:05.467
Libros para
los muertos.

22:07.100 --> 22:10.033
- Hey, Rebadow, man,
I'll take a novel.

22:10.100 --> 22:12.567
